rest api ->  a type of API that follows the design principles of REST, it allows applications to communicate with each other over the internet, 
using standard HTTP methods like GET, POST, PUT, and DELETE 

nodejs vs js -> js is a scripting language , that provides/enables dynamic content and interactivity on websites
                node js is a run time environment , that allows the js to run outside the browser. in backend
